{"tid":2375536,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"粉絲向GFRIEND透露自己的苦惱... 反遭嚴智語重心長的回答：「你該反省！」","createTime":"2021-01-22T06:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T16:17:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"85868504bf713dd04e8c77675bb2449dc55cead2","tid":2375536,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/21/550_1559103_1611223949.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F21%2F550_1559103_1611223949.webp&h=cee36a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n追星本生是件有趣且幸福的是，偶像可以給粉絲帶來動力與快樂，但若是過於沈迷可會帶來不好的結果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/21/550_1559102_1611223939.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F21%2F550_1559102_1611223939.webp&h=49584a48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本月五日GFRIEND成員嚴智在直播時，有位粉絲留言向他表達了自己的苦惱：「現在是放假期間，處於暫停學習的狀態，所以一直沈迷在GFRIEND的weverse（與偶像溝通的APP），但父母唸說要背點英語。」<br />\n<br />\n對此，嚴智並沒有安慰粉絲，反而向這位粉絲說：「與其說這是煩惱，更像是需要反省的事情。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/21/550_1559107_1611223965.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F21%2F550_1559107_1611223965.webp&h=62cfa207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同時嚴智提到粉絲的父母要求背英語的行為並不過分，粉絲的苦惱也不值得體諒。若粉絲連背英語都覺得煩惱，是不敢處於對於現實太過懶惰的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n並語重心長的說：「如果粉絲是以這種狀態沈迷我們的話，我們無法體會到自己工作的價值。<br />\n<br />\n嚴智說希望自己能給粉絲帶來安慰、幸福，而不是妨礙。而且她也對27歲粉絲的未來感到擔憂，最後她還讓粉絲過好自己的人生，偶爾去看看她們就好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/21/550_1559108_1611223975.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F21%2F550_1559108_1611223975.webp&h=f192b918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嚴智的一番話，讓網友們非常讚賞他智慧的說法，並紛紛表示不能因為追星而迷失了自己的人生，過分或盲目地追星，會帶來很多負面影響。"},{"pid":"51dda783a76a8088af0031afa43b9f758b84fd90","tid":2375536,"uid":136738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"好女仔不過似幾chur"},{"pid":"c1e70687b24170a1f4d343a9c8d1bddb5584ffbc","tid":2375536,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51dda783a76a8088af0031afa43b9f758b84fd90","tid":2375536,"uid":136738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"好女仔不過似幾chur"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"講乜撚野牙你"},{"pid":"8af4f949a2a20f201522875c1e27f4396e76fa47","tid":2375536,"uid":190258,"like":15,"dislike":26,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"傻仔先沉gfriend 抵鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8abf6581b6c25d86b005a98973ace55351036a","tid":2375536,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"P牌朴彩英可以入黎呢度"},{"pid":"51138914008f70f33e0d13a8bcb5f5e37e93ab09","tid":2375536,"uid":74065,"like":13,"dislike":10,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8af4f949a2a20f201522875c1e27f4396e76fa47","tid":2375536,"uid":190258,"like":15,"dislike":26,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"傻仔先沉gfriend 抵鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:17:18.000Z","msg":"造假團🤷&zwj;♂️你咪繼續酸"},{"pid":"d53dfae6b824077e0dab38c38478441fbecd37e0","tid":2375536,"uid":58335,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:19:43.000Z","msg":"心地幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a0f3c8d7591f5148badf16bc21a1e3a1bc0184","tid":2375536,"uid":2781,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"umji<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2479b089cd5ec18516d30bebb8a78c32bc742ea5","tid":2375536,"uid":384468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:26:17.000Z","msg